com.amazonaws.services.s3.model.analytics

Class AnalyticsFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.s3.model.analytics.AnalyticsFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AnalyticsFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The filter used to describe a set of objects for analysis. The analytics filter contains one of AnalyticsPrefixPredicate, AnalyticsTagPredicate or AnalyticsAndOperator. If no filter is provided, all objects will be considered for analysis.
